{
  "texts": [
    "Participants were instructed to carefully read all scenarios which were presented in random order.",
    "Afterwards, we assessed participants' attitudes toward AI.",
    "Hence, we inquired about their frequency of using AI-based tools (response options: never, rarely, occasionally, frequently, very frequently), their perception of AI's impact on healthcare (response options: no, minor, moderate, significant, highly significant) and whether they view the integration of AI in healthcare as presenting more risks or opportunities (response options: more risks, neutral, more opportunities).",
    "Finally, we collected demographic information on gender, age, educational level, and nationality.",
    "We preregistered our analysis plan, data collection strategy, and the experimental design (https://osf.io/6trux)."
  ]
}